This example is using Tsdl for graphical output and UI. The image is in BMP 
(RGB, 8 bit per channel) format.

Install SDL2 library (https://www.libsdl.org/) for your system first.

To install Tsdl package:
    opam install tsdl

To build:
    make

To use:
    ./main

Controls: 

Left Arrow Key / A to move Left
Right Arrow Key / D to move Right
Spacebar to shoot 

`Esc` or `Q`: exit

![](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/25540795/56857479-20c13d00-693c-11e9-827f-6e6ed5b735c8.gif)
